name: Ext_R4_AuditEvent_outcome
title: Cross-version Extension for R4.AuditEvent.outcome for use in FHIR R5
description: This cross-version extension represents AuditEvent.outcome from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/AuditEvent|4.0.1 for use in FHIR R5.

element.short: Whether the event succeeded or failed
element.definition: Indicates whether the event succeeded or failed.
element.comment: `AuditEvent.outcome` maps to R5 `AuditEvent.outcome`. Has no type mapping `outcome` removed the required value set binding to `http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/audit-event-outcome|4.3.0`. So is mapped as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget.
